(10, '1565430340_5d4e9244a026b.jpeg', '1565250166_5d4bd276e1ee0.jpeg', 'Center for Specialised Care and Research (CSCR)', 'Endeavour for ONE STOP Medical Service', 'Location: 1675/A, O.R Nizam Road, Chittagong. info@cscrbd.com', '01727069922', NULL, 'Who We Are?\n \nCenter for Specialised Care & Research (CSCR) is a medical institution dedicated to provide quality patient care with unrelenting attention to clinical excellence,patient safety and unparalleled passion and commitment to assure the very best healthcare for those we serve.\n\nOur Mission: \n \nCSCR (Pvt) Ltd. The widely referred to clinical lab service center since 1999 has become the symbol of patient care in terms of precision and accuracy in diagnostic laboratory services round-the-clock. Equipped with most modern and state-of-art equipment and machinery, this international standard facility provides world-class diagnostic services. Besides, it facilities consultation services to the patient by renowned physicians and surgeons of the country.\nCSCR (Pvt) Ltd. Jas earned the confidences of patients and physicians for very high quality, prompt and reliable diagnostic services for various diseases including the cardiac enzymes on emergency basis and molecular diagnosis lab tests, besides the common clinical lab tests.\nThe lab facilities are open to the general public 24 hours a day and 7-days a week that makes ot the only diagnostic center in Bangladesh to do so. Quality assurance and the laboratory information system are integral parts of CSCR laboratory functions.\nAll lab staff works under close supervision of highly trained and reputed consultants of different specialties i.e. Pathologists, Hematologists, Histopathology’s, Microbiologist, Immunologist, Biochemist, Molecular Biologist and Laboratory Manager ensure reliability and promptness of test and disposal of test results.', 47, 2, 0, 'Specialised Care for all types of Patients.', 'Medical Treatment, Emergency Help, Medical Checkup, Qualified Doctors.', 'Specialists\nOur Emergency Department is one of the best in city including Minor Operation Theatre. We provide 24 hours service. Renowned Professor and Physicians are available here.\n04 bedded Emergency care including 01 HDU bed facility\n24 hours service by trained doctors and nurses care.\n24 hours Bed side Echocardiogram, USG, X-ray and pathological support within unit.\n24 hours Indoor Pharmacy service\n24 Hours uninterrupted power supply.\nCentral Oxygen, Nitrous and Air supply.\nMedical board facilities with renowned consultants.\nBlood transfusion facilities on outdoor basis.\nVarious minor operation, observation and procedures are done here.', 'http://cscrbd.com', 0, '2019-08-08 07:26:03', '2019-09-09 09:16:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(12, '1574066084_5dd257a4d5f69.jpeg', '1574066085_5dd257a5d9511.png', 'Qrex', NULL, 'Port Connecting Road, G block, Halishahar', '031 717090', NULL, 'Qrex diagnostic centre and consultancy is a private owned limited company based in the city of Chittagong in Bangladesh. Qrex diagnostic centre and consultancy was established to provide first class independent health care to our local community. Qrex was established keeping in mind the dream of all medical diagnostic facilities under one roof.\n\nWe believe in providing quality services and excellent hospitality. Here we focus on excellence and committed to patient care. We maintain an attitude of zero tolerance towards standard Quality Work resulting in only the best Images, world class services and qualitative reports. Our expert group of employees and consultant doctors makes it all possible.\n\nWe try providing integrated healthcare by working hand-in-hand with community partners, patients, caregivers and staff. Within the whole realm of healthcare, helping people to stay healthy is a priority. Hence, one of our pillars of our mission is to help the community stay well. When individuals fall sick, we will heal them to the best of our ability. This is the traditional role of diagnostic centres and we must continue to excel in this area of care.\n\nQrex is the dream of young entrepreneurs who united to build up a brand. A particular brand which will be loved and praised by people for their professionalism and hospitality. The core intent was to bring the latest world-class, state-of-the-art diagnostic technologies to the service of patients.\n\nAt qrex, patient’s welfare is the priority. We treat each and every patient with dignity.\n\nHere we use modern most up to date equipments for our reliable reports. We provide an ideal environment for the comprehensive approach that is needed for the effective treatment .Quality services in affordable prices for the welfare of the community for a better tomorrow is our target.', 42, 2, 0, 'Diagnostic Center with modern age technological support', 'We are committed:- * To providing quality holistic and compassionate care to our patients. * To create state of the art healthcare services for our custome', 'Various renowned doctors are practicing here.', 'http://', 0, '2019-11-18 08:34:46', '2019-11-18 08:34:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
